  "texts": [
    "There is a growing amount of literature highlighting the relationship between investment, business and market.",
    "The literature can be divided into three strands to show the relationship between these entities:",
    "• Investment and Business relationship: Investments are assets or funds invested in a company with an expectation of long-term growth specifically through M &A or becoming an IPO (Pan et al. 2018).",
    "Ideally, the investment journey starts with planning and strategy.",
    "There is always a time frame associated with any investments which can be fruitful in long-term planning."
  ]
}